rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Unconstrained properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators without specific or implicit restrictions to RDA entities.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abbreviatedTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abbreviated title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title that has been abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that shortens a source resource without changing a general meaning or manner of presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abridged, i.e., shortened without changing a general meaning or manner of presentation of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abridger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing an original resource but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing an original resource but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbed agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that was absorbed by another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates part of the content of another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbingAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbing agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that absorbed another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been partially incorporated into another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been incorporated into another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that abbreviates a source resource in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an abstracting and indexing service that abstracts the contents of a source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractsFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose contents have been abstracted by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: academicDegree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic degree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accessibilityContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accessibility content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of content that provides alternative sensory modes to perceive a primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Accessibility content includes accessible labels, audio description, captioning, image description, sign language, and subtitles. Accessibility content does not include subtitles in a language different from the spoken content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompaniedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource issued with another resource, without any relationship to its content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompanyingResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an augmentation of, or is augmented by, or is complemented by, or accompanies, or is accompanied by a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that modifies a source resource for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPicture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a motion picture based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a radio program based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioScript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a script for a radio program, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a television program based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a television program, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a video based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a video, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsChoreography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as choreography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of movement based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsGraphicNovel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as graphic novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a graphic novel based on a source resource

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsLibretto
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a text of an opera or other resource for a musical stage, or an oratorio, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsMusicalTheatre
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as musical theatre
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical theatre resource based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOpera
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an opera based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOratorio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as oratorio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an oratorio based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsVideoGame
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video game
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to relates a resource to a video game based on a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedInVerseAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted in verse as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a literary composition in verse form adapted from a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addenda
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of brief content that is essential for the completeness of another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is completed with brief content from another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: additionalScaleInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has additional scale information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of supplemental information about scale.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Statement of comparative measurements or limitation of the scale to particular parts of the content of a resource are included.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addressee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addresseeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addressee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an address of an agent's place of residence, business, or employer, headquarters or offices, or an e-mail or internet address.

rdf:Description.reg:name: affiliation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has affiliation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a group with which an agent is affiliated or has been affiliated through employment, membership, cultural identity, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: agentHistory
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has agent history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to biographical or historical information about an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alsoIssuedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is also issued as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that carries the same content of a resource in a different format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternateIdentity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternate identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a pseudonymous or other identity assumed by an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeChronologicalDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative chronological designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in the form of a date on the first issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year. An alternative chronological designation may include a date in a different calendar.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeChronologicalDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative chronological designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in the form of a date on the last issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designational includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year. An alternative chronological designation may include a date in a different calendar.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeNumericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative numeric and/or alphabetic designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in numeric or alphabetic form on the first issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeNumericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative numeric and/or alphabetic designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in numeric or alphabetic form on the last issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that examines a source resource to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysisOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has animator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a moving image resource or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of the drawings that are animated is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is animator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a moving image resource or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of the drawings that are animated is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has annotator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who makes manuscript annotations on a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is annotator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who makes manuscript annotations on a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who appeals a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who appeals a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent against whom an appeal is taken on a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent against whom an appeal is taken on a decision of a lower court recorded in a legal resource of a higher court to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendix
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content augments another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is augmented with content from another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appliedMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has applied material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architect
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc., will look when completed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architectOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is architect of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc., will look when completed to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranged as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that rewrites a source resource for a medium of performance different from that for which a resource was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arrangement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that has been rewritten for a medium of performance different from that for which a resource was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has arranger of music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a musical resource by rewriting a composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a resource was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Modification of the resource for the same medium of performance, etc., keeping the musical substance of the original composition essentially unchanged, is included. Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new musical resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusicOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranger of music of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a musical resource by rewriting a composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a resource was originally intended to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has art director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by overseeing artists and craftspeople who build sets for moving image productions.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is art director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by overseeing artists and craftspeople who build sets for moving image productions to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: aspectRatio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has aspect ratio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a numerical ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: aspectRatioDesignation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has aspect ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a general designation of the ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: assistant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has assistant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a colleague who helps another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: assistantTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is assistant to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a colleague who is helped by another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: associatedInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has associated institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an institution commonly associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: audioEngineer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has audio engineer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to the audio content of a resource by managing the technical aspects of sound during the processes of recording, mixing, and reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: audioEngineerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is audio engineer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution to the audio content of managing the technical aspects of sound during the processes of recording, mixing, and reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: audioProducer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has audio producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a producer responsible for most of the business aspects of an audio recording.

rdf:Description.reg:name: audioProducerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is audio producer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that involves a responsibility for most of the business aspects of an audio recording.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmentation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is added to by another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmented by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that adds to the content of a predominant resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: author
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has author
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type or genre.

rdf:Description.reg:name: authorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is author of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type or genre to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has autographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent whose manuscript signature appears on a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is autographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent whose manuscript signature appears on a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: award
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has award
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a formal recognition of excellence, etc., given by an award- or prize-granting body, for the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a source for a derivative resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: baseMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has base material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an underlying physical material of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bibliographicFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has bibliographic format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a proportional relationship between a whole sheet in a printed or manuscript resource, and the individual leaves that result if that sheet is left full, cut, or folded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has binder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who binds a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binderOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is binder of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who binds a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: biographicalInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has biographical information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a summary of information about the life or history of an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookArtist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has book artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an artist responsible for creating art resources that exploit a book form or alter its physical structure as part of a content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookArtistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is book artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an artist responsible for creating art resources that exploit a book form or alter its physical structure as part of the content of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has book designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is book designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: boundWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is bound with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been bound within the same binding as a resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: brailleEmbosser
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has braille embosser
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device.

rdf:Description.reg:name: brailleEmbosserOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is braille embosser of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcaster
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has broadcaster
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in broadcasting a resource to an audience via radio, television, webcast, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcasterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is broadcaster of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in broadcasting a resource to an audience via radio, television, webcast, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcastStandard
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has broadcast standard
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a system used to format a video resource for television broadcast.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broaderAffiliatedAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has broader affiliated agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that acts for a local affiliated agent and others at a broader organizational level to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenza
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource consisting of an ornamental passage for a soloist, added to a musical resource such as a concerto, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenzaComposedFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza composed for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource such as a concerto for which an ornamental passage for a soloist has been composed, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: calligrapher
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has calligrapher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an artist responsible for creating a resource of calligraphy where a focus of interest lies in the aesthetic value of its penmanship or graphic artistry, regardless of whether the same agent also authored the inscribed text.

rdf:Description.reg:name: calligrapherOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is calligrapher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an artist responsible for creating a resource of calligraphy where a focus of interest lies in the aesthetic value of its penmanship or graphic artistry, regardless of whether the same agent also authored the inscribed text to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: captureInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has capture information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a place, date, or other information associated with the recording, filming, etc., of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: carrierType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has carrier type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting a format of a storage medium and housing of a carrier in combination with a type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has cartographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cartographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographicDataType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has cartographic data type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a machine-readable representation of geospatial features.

rdf:Description.reg:name: caster
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has caster
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: casterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is caster of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: castingDIrector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has casting director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for most aspects of assigning parts and duties to performers.

rdf:Description.reg:name: castingDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is casting director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution of responsibility for most aspects of assigning parts and duties to performers.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogue
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of a complete enumeration of resources arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a catalogue, i.e., a complete enumeration of resources arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: censor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has censor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by revising the content for the purpose of suppressing parts deemed objectionable on moral, political, military, or other grounds, but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: censorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is censor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by revising the content for the purpose of suppressing parts deemed objectionable on moral, political, military, or other grounds, but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: chiefExecutive
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has chief executive
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an officer who is a top ranking official of an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: chiefExecutiveOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is chief executive of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent in which an officer is a top ranking official.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choralConductor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has choral conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a conductor contributing to a musical resource by leading a choral performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choralConductorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choral conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a conductor contributing to a musical resource by leading a choral performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has choreographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource of movement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource of movement to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographicAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreographic adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a resource consisting of movement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides choreography for use in a related resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses choreography of a related resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: chronologicalDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has chronological designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in date form presented on the first issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year.

rdf:Description.reg:name: chronologicalDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has chronological designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in date form presented on the last issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colleague
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colleague
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a fellow member of a profession, staff, or academic faculty.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrar
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collection registrar
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a curator who lists or inventories resources in an aggregate resource such as a collection of resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrarOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collection registrar of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a curator who lists or inventories resources in an aggregate resource such as a collection of resources to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collector
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a curator who brings together resources from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collector of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a curator who brings together resources from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collotyper
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collotyper
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource using a photomechanical process for making prints directly from a hardened film of gelatin or other colloid that has ink-receptive and ink-repellent surfaces.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collotyperOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collotyper of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource using a photomechanical process for making prints directly from a hardened film of gelatin or other colloid that has ink-receptive and ink-repellent surfaces to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a presence of colour, tone, etc., in the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Black, white, single colour shades of black, single colour tints of white, and single colour tones of gray are considered to be single colours.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colourist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by applying colour to drawings, prints, photographs, maps, moving images, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colouristOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is colourist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by applying colour to drawings, prints, photographs, maps, moving images, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commemoration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commemoration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource created to commemorate an earlier resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commemorationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commemoration of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource commemorated in a later resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on a described resource

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commentator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commissioningBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commissioning body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for commissioning a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commissioningBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commissioning body of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for commissioning a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compiler
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has compiler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a new resource such as a bibliography or a directory by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Revising or clarifying the content, or selecting and putting together resources or parts of resources, by one or more creators is excluded

rdf:Description.reg:name: compilerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is compiler of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a new resource such as a bibliography or a directory by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc., to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: complementedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is complemented by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource paired with another resource without either resource being considered to predominate.

rdf:Description.reg:name: componentOfMerger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has component of merger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that formed another agent by merging with one or more other agents to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has composer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a musical resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Adaptation of another musical resource to form a distinct alteration, paraphrasing a resource or creating a resource in the general style of another composer, or creating a resource that is based on the music of another composer, is included.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is composer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a musical resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordance
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of an index of all a words in a predominant resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a concordance, i.e. an index of all the words in the predominant resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a musical resource by leading a performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a musical resource by leading a performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: configurationOfPlaybackChannels
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has configuration of playback channels
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a number of sound channels used to make a recording.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has consultant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another agent that is represented as a creator of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is consultant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another agent that is represented as a creator of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contactInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has contact information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name, address, etc., of an organization, etc., from which a resource may be obtained.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contact information includes the name, address, etc. of the publisher, distributor, etc. of a published resource, or of the archival repository that holds the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a larger resource of which a part is a discrete component.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is container of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a discrete component of a larger resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contentType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has content type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting a fundamental form of communication in which a content is expressed and a human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Content type also reflects the number of spatial dimensions and the presence or absence of movement in which content expressed in the form of an image or images is intended to be perceived.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that split into two or more separate resources with new titles.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is continued by the content of a later resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content continues an earlier resource under a new title.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource part of whose content separated from an earlier resource to form a new resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has contributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contributors include editors, translators, arrangers of music, performers, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to an expression to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coordinatesOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coordinates of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a mathematical system for identifying an area covered by the cartographic content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: copyrightDate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has copyright date
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has costume designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by designing costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is costume designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by designing costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: countryAssociatedWithAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has country associated with agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a country with which an agent is identified.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGoverned
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGovernedOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court governed of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court reporter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by preparing a court's opinions for publication.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court reporter of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by preparing a court's opinions for publication to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coverageOfContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coverage of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a chronological or geographic coverage of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coworker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has co-worker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a colleague who works with or shares a task with another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has creator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for the creation of a resource
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creators include agents who are jointly responsible for the creation of a resource either performing the same role, such as in a collaboration between two writers, or performing different roles, such as in a collaboration between a composer and a lyricist.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is creator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the creation of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiquedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critiqued in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that contains a critical evaluation of a described resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiqueOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critique of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a critical evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has curator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent conceiving, aggregating, or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is curator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent conceiving, aggregating, or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has current owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent currently having legal possession of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwnerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is current owner of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent currently having legal possession of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodialHistoryOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodial history of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a record of previous ownership or custodianship of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodian
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodian
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent having legal custody of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodianOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is custodian of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent having legal custody of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dancer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dancer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by dancing in a musical, dramatic, etc., presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dancerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dancer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by dancing in a musical, dramatic, etc., presentation to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateAssociatedWithAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date associated with agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a significant date associated with the history of an agent, or the date or range of dates on which a conference, etc., was held, or a date with which an agent is otherwise associated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfBirth
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of birth
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a year an agent was born.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with the recording, filming, etc., of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfConferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of conference, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date or range of dates on which a conference, congress, meeting, exhibition, fair, festival, etc., was held.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfDeath
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of death
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a year an agent died.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfDistribution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of distribution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with the distribution of a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfEstablishment
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of establishment
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date on which an agent was established or founded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfManufacture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of manufacture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfProduction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of production
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of a resource in an unpublished form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfPublication
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of publication
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with the publication, release, or issuing of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an earliest date associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfTermination
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of termination
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date on which an agent was terminated or dissolved.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfUsage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of usage
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a name to a date or range of dates associated with the use of the name chosen as a preferred name for an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: declination
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has declination
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an angular distance to a body on the celestial sphere measured north or south through 90 from the celestial equator along the hour circle of the body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicatee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicatee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent to whom a resource is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicateeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dedicatee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to whom a resource is dedicated to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent by whom a resource is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dedicator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent by whom a resource is dedicated to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: defendant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has defendant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who is accused in a criminal proceeding or sued in a civil proceeding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: defendantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is defendant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who is accused in a criminal proceeding or sued in a civil proceeding to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeCommitteeMember
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has degree committee member
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent serving on a committee that supervises a students thesis or dissertation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeCommitteeMemberOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is degree committee member of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent serving on a committee that supervises a students thesis or dissertation to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeGrantingInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has degree granting institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent granting an academic degree.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeGrantingInstitutionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is degree granting institution of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent granting an academic degree to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeSupervisor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has degree supervisor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent, such as an advisor or supervisor of thesis or dissertation research, overseeing either an academic degree or thesis.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeSupervisorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is degree supervisor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent, such as an advisor or supervisor of thesis or dissertation research, overseeing either an academic degree or thesis to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: depositor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has depositor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a current owner of a resource who deposited a resource into the custody of another agent, while still retaining ownership.

rdf:Description.reg:name: depositorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is depositor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a current owner of a resource who deposited a resource into the custody of another agent, while still retaining ownership to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: derivative
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is derivative
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a modification of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: derivativeResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has derivative resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is based on or is a derivative of another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: describedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is described in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that describes a described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descriptionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is description of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource described by a describing entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: designationOfEdition
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designation of edition

rdf:Description.reg:name: designationOfNamedRevisionOfEdition
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designation of named revision of edition
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character or group of words or characters, identifying a particular revision of a named edition.

rdf:Description.reg:name: designer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a design for an object.

rdf:Description.reg:name: designerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a design for an object to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfAppliedMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of applied material
