rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfAspectRatioDesignation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of aspect ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfBaseMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of base material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an underlying physical material of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfBibliographicFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of bibliographic format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the proportional relationship between a whole sheet in a printed or manuscript resource, and the individual leaves that result if that sheet is left full, cut, or folded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfBroadcastStandard
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of broadcast standard
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a system used to format a video resource for television broadcast.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfCartographicDataType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of cartographic data type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a machine-readable representation of geospatial features.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfColourContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of colour content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the presence of colour, tone, etc., in the content of a resource, and the specific colours, tones, etc., including black and white, present.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfConfigurationOfPlaybackChannels
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of configuration of playback channels
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a number of sound channels used to make a recording.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfDigitalFileCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of digital file characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to a digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfDigitalRepresentationOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of digital representation of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfDuration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of duration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the playing time, running time, performance time, etc., of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfEmulsionOnMicrofilmAndMicrofiche
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of emulsion on microfilm and microfiche
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a suspension of light-sensitive chemicals used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfEncodingFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of encoding format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a schema, standard, etc., used to encode the digital content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFileType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of file type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a general type of data content encoded in a computer file.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFontSize
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of font size
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a size of the type used to represent characters and symbols in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormatOfNotatedMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of format of notated music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a musical or physical layout of the content of a resource that is presented in a form of musical notation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfMusicalNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of musical notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express musical content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfNotatedMovement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of notated movement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express movement content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfTactileNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of tactile notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of a resource in a form that can be perceived through touch.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGeneration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship between an original carrier and a carrier of a reproduction made from an original.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfAudioRecording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original audio carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a tape duplication master, a test pressing).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfDigitalResource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a digital resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a derivative master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfMicroform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original microform carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a printing master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a motion picture film resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a reference print).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfVideotape
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a videotape resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a show copy).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGrooveCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of groove characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a groove width of an analog disc or a groove pitch of an analog cylinder.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfIllustrativeContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of content intended to illustrate a primary content of a resource.
Relates a resource to details of a presence of one or more still images that accompany the primary content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfLayout
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfMount
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of mount
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource has been attached.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPlayingSpeed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of playing speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which an audio carrier must be operated to produce the sound intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPolarity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of polarity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship of the colours and tones in an image to the colours and tones of the object reproduced.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPresentationFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of presentation format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a format used in the production of a projected image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProductionMethod
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of production method
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a process used to produce a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProjectionCharacteristicOfMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of projection characteristic of motion picture film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProjectionSpeed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of projection speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which a projected carrier must be operated to produce the moving image intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfRecordingMedium
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of recording medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a type of medium used to record sound on an audio carrier.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfReductionRatioDesignation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of reduction ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a designation of the size of a micro-image to an original from which it was produced.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of regional encoding
rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfRegionalEncoding
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier has been encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfScript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of set of characters or symbols used to express written language content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfSoundCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of sound characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfSpecialPlaybackCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of special playback characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an equalization system, noise reduction system, etc., used in making an audio recording.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTapeConfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of tape configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a number of tracks on an audiotape.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTrackConfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of track configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a configuration of the audio track on a sound-track film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTypeOfRecording
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of type of recording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a method used to encode audio content for playback.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfVideoCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to an encoding of video images in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfVideoFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a standard, etc., used to encode the analog video content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digested as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that systematically and comprehensively condenses a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been digested, i.e., systematically and comprehensively condensed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalFileCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital file characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a technical specification relating to a digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalRepresentationOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital representation of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of technical details relating to an encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransfer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital transfer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that results from a transfer of a resource in another digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransferOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensions
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a carrier or a container of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensionsOfMapEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of map, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a face of a map, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensionsOfStillImage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of still image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of the pictorial area of a still image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: director
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director of photography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges lighting. a director of photography for a movie is also called a chief cinematographer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotographyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of photography of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges lighting. a director of photography for a movie is also called a chief cinematographer to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dissertationOrThesisInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dissertation or thesis information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying an academic institution, degree, and year for which a resource was presented.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying a place or places of distribution, distributor or distributors, and date or dates of distribution of a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for distributing a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is distributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for distributing a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributorsName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distributors name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of an agent responsible for distributing a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: DJ
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has DJ
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who mixes recorded tracks together during a live performance or in a recording studio to appear as one continuous track.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, and mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: DJOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is DJ of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution of mixing recorded tracks together during a live performance or in a recording studio to appear as one continuous track.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, and mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has donor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a former owner of a resource who donated that resource to another owner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is donor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a former owner of a resource who donated that resource to another owner to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: draftsman
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has draftsman
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by an architect, inventor, etc., by making detailed plans or drawings for buildings, ships, aircraft, machines, objects, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: draftsmanOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is draftsman of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by an architect, inventor, etc., by making detailed plans or drawings for buildings, ships, aircraft, machines, objects, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatization of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a drama.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatized as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a dramatic resource adapted from a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbedVersion
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dubbed version
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a moving image resource that translates spoken dialogue of an original resource into a different language.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbedVersionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dubbed version of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a moving image resource in which spoken dialogue has been translated into a language different from that of an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbingDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dubbing director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for the general management and supervision of the process of adding new dialogue or other sounds to complete a sound track for a resource

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbingDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dubbing director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution of responsibility for the general management and supervision of the process of adding new dialogue or other sounds to complete a sound track.

rdf:Description.reg:name: duration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has duration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a playing time, running time, etc., of a content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: earlierTitleProper
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has earlier title proper
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title proper appearing on an earlier iteration of an integrating resource that differs from that on a current iteration.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has edition statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying an edition to which a resource belongs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has editor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by revising or clarifying the content, or by selecting and putting together resources, or parts of resources, by one or more creators.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Addition of an introduction, notes, or other critical matter, or preparing a resource for production, publication, or distribution is included. Major revision, adaptation, etc., that substantially changes the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorialDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has editorial director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent having legal or intellectual responsibility other than creation for the content of a serial, integrating resource, or multipart monographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorialDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is editorial director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for a legal or intellectual responsibility other than creation for the content of a serial, integrating resource, or multipart monographic resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is editor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by revising or clarifying the content, e.g., adding an introduction, notes, or other critical matter to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOfMovingImageResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has editor of moving image work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for assembling, arranging, and trimming film, video, or other moving image formats, including both visual and audio aspects.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOfMovingImageResourceOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is editor of moving image resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for assembling, arranging, and trimming film, video, or other moving image formats, including both visual and audio aspects to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: electronicReproduction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has electronic reproduction
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that is a result of a transfer of a resource in an analog format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: electronicReproductionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is electronic reproduction of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in an analog format that is transferred to a digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: employee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has employee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent employed by an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: employer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has employer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that employs an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: emulsionOnMicrofilmAndMicrofiche
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has emulsion on microfilm and microfiche
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a suspension of light-sensitive chemicals used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche.

rdf:Description.reg:name: enactingJurisdiction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has enacting jurisdiction
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a jurisdiction enacting a law, regulation, constitution, court rule, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: enactingJurisdictionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is enacting jurisdiction of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a jurisdiction enacting a law, regulation, constitution, court rule, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: encodedBitrate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has encoded bitrate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a speed at which streaming audio, video, etc., is designed to play.

rdf:Description.reg:name: encodingFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has encoding format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a schema, standard, etc., used to encode the digital content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: engraver
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has engraver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by cutting letters, figures, etc., on a surface such as a wooden or metal plate used for printing.

rdf:Description.reg:name: engraverOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is engraver of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by cutting letters, figures, etc., on a surface such as a wooden or metal plate used for printing to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: enrolledStudent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has enrolled student
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who receives instruction at an educational institution.

rdf:Description.reg:name: epoch
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has epoch
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an arbitrary moment in time to which measurements of position for a body or orientation for an orbit are referred.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equinox
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equinox
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a point of intersection of the ecliptic and the celestial equator, occupied by the sun when its declination is 0.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equipmentOrSystemRequirement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equipment or system requirement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a system or equipment required for use, playback, etc., of an analog, digital, etc., resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equivalent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equivalent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that carries the same content as a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equivalentResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equivalent resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is equivalent to another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errata
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of errors discovered after the publication of a predominant resource, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errataTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is augmented by a list of errors in a predominant resource, discovered after publication, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: etcher
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has etcher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by subjecting metal, glass, or some other surface used for printing, to acid or another corrosive substance.

rdf:Description.reg:name: etcherOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is etcher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by subjecting metal, glass, or some other surface used for printing, to acid or another corrosive substance to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluatedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluated in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that examines or judges a described resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is examined or judged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that enlarges upon the content of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedVersionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded version of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a derivative resource that enlarges upon the content of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: extent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has extent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a number and type of unit or subunit of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimile
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has facsimile
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that exactly reproduces another resource embodying a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimileContainedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is facsimile contained in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a larger resource of which a part is a discrete component that exactly reproduces another resource embodying a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimileContainerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is facsimile container of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for an exact reproduction that is a discrete component of a larger entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fileSize

rdf:Description.reg:name: fileType

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDirector

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDirectorOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDistributorOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmedWith

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmmaker

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmmakerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmProducer

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmProducerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAid

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides a guide to an organization, arrangement, and contents of an archival collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAidFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is finding aid for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an archival collection that is described in a finding aid, i.e., a guide to an organization, arrangement, and contents of a collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fontSize
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has font size
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a size of the type used to represent characters and symbols in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formatOfNotatedMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has format of notated music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical or physical layout of the content of a resource that is presented in the form of musical notation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formerOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has former owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent formerly having legal possession of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formerOwnerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfMusicalNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of musical notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of characters or symbols used to express musical content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfNotatedMovement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of notated movement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of characters or symbols used to express movement content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a class or genre to which a resource belongs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfTactileNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of tactile notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of a resource in a form that can be perceived through touch.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundedEntity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founded entity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that an agent founded to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: founder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who founded an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: founderOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founder of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for establishing a serial, integrating resource, or multipart monographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: founderOfResourceOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is founder of resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for establishing a serial, integrating resource, or multipart monograph to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freelyTranslatedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is freely translated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is both an adaptation and a translation into another language of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freeTranslationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is free translation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted and translated into another language.

rdf:Description.reg:name: frequency
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has frequency
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an interval at which an issue or part of a serial or an update to an integrating resource is issued.

rdf:Description.reg:name: friend
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has friend
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who shares a bond of mutual affection or regard with another agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fullerFormOfName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has fuller form of name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a full form of a part of a name represented only by an initial or abbreviation in a form chosen as a preferred name, or a part of a name not included in a form chosen as a preferred name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: gender
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has gender
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a gender with which an agent identifies.

rdf:Description.reg:name: generation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a relationship between an original carrier and a carrier of a reproduction made from an original.

rdf:Description.reg:name: generationOfAudioRecording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the relationship between an original audio carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a tape duplication master, a test pressing).

rdf:Description.reg:name: generationOfDigitalResource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the relationship between an original carrier of a digital resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a derivative master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: generationOfMicroform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the relationship between an original microform carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a printing master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: generationOfMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the relationship between an original carrier of a motion picture film resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a reference print).

rdf:Description.reg:name: generationOfVideotape
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the relationship between an original carrier of a videotape resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a show copy).

rdf:Description.reg:name: givenName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has given name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a name given to an agent at birth or at some later point in addition to, or instead of, a surname.

rdf:Description.reg:name: graduate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has graduate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent who receives an academic degree from a granting institution or faculty.

rdf:Description.reg:name: graduateOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is graduate of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an institution or faculty that granted an academic degree to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: grantingInstitutionOrFaculty
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has granting institution or faculty
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an institution or faculty conferring an academic degree on a candidate.

rdf:Description.reg:name: graphicNovelizationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is graphic novelization of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resourcce to a resource that has been adapted as a graphic novel.

rdf:Description.reg:name: grooveCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has groove characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a groove width of an analog disc or a groove pitch of an analog cylinder.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guide
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that guides a user through the use of a predominant resource, using notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guideTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is augmented by another resource consisting of material, such as notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc., to help a user of a predominant resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hereditaryTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hereditary title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title of nobility, etc., associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hierarchicalSubordinate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hierarchical subordinate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that is subordinate to another agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hierarchicalSuperior
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hierarchical superior
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that is hierarchically superior to another agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: historyOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has history of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a summary of information about the history of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honouree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has honouree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent honoured by a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honoureeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is honouree of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent honoured by a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: horizontalScaleOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has horizontal scale of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a ratio of horizontal distances in the cartographic content of a resource to the actual distances they represent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: host
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has host
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by leading a program, often broadcast, that includes other guests, performers, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: host institution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has host institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent hosting the event, exhibit, conference, etc., which gave rise to a resource, but having little or no responsibility for the content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hostInstitutionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is host institution of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent hosting an event, exhibit, conference, etc., which gave rise to a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hostOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is host of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by leading a program, often broadcast, that includes other guests, performers, etc., to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a character string uniquely associated with an agent, or with a surrogate for an agent such as an authority record.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a character string associated with a resource that serves to differentiate a resource from other resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illuminator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illuminator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent providing decoration to a specific resource using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illuminatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illuminator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent providing decoration to a specific resource using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrations
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate an augmented resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrationsFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is augmented by pictorial content designed to explain or decorate it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrativeContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a presence of one or more still images that accompany a primary content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by supplementing a primary content with drawings, diagrams, photographs, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of content that is primarily artistic is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustratorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by supplementing a primary content with drawings, diagrams, photographs, etc. to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creation of content that is primarily artistic is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitatedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that copies the style or content of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose style or content is copied in a derivative resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: immediateSourceOfAcquisitionOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has immediate source of acquisition of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a source from which an agency directly acquired a resource and the circumstances under which it was received.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that provides incidental music for a play or other spoken resource for the stage.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusicFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource such as a play or other spoken resource for the stage that uses a musical resource as incidental music.

rdf:Description.reg:name: index
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of a predominant resource, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexed in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an abstracting and indexing service that indexes the contents of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexingFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexing for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose contents have been indexed by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for an index, i.e., a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of a predominant resource, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inscriber
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inscriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who has written a statement of dedication or gift on a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inscriberOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inscriber of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who has written a statement of dedication or gift on a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is in series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in which a part has been issued; a title of a larger resource appears on a part.

rdf:Description.reg:name: insert
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is insert
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in which a part has been issued; a title of a larger resource appears on a part.

rdf:Description.reg:name: insertedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inserted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource into which material has been inserted that is not an integral part of the publication.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inspirationFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inspiration for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource which was inspired by another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inspiredBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inspired by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource which serves as the inspiration for another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: instrumentalConductor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instrumental conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a conductor contributing to a musical resource by leading an instrumental performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: instrumentalConductorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is instrumental conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a conductor contributing to a musical resource by leading an instrumental performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource

rdf:Description.reg:name: instrumentalist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instrumentalist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by playing a musical instrument.

rdf:Description.reg:name: instrumentalistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is instrumentalist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by playing a musical instrument to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: intendedAudience
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has intended audience
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a category of user for which the content of a resource is intended, or for whom the content is considered suitable.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: intervieweeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is interviewee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is interviewer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inventor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inventor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a new device or process.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inventorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is inventor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a new device or process to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issnOfSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has ISSN of series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an identifier assigned to a series by an ISSN registration agency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issnOfSubseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has ISSN of subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an identifier assigned to a subseries by an ISSN registration agency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issuedWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is issued with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is issued on the same carrier as a resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issuingBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has issuing body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent issuing a resource, such as an official organ of the agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issuingBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is issuing body of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent issuing a resource, such as an official organ of the agent, to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: jointlyHeldConference
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has jointly held conference
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a conference to a conference that is jointly held with another conference.

rdf:Description.reg:name: judge
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has judge
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who hears and decides on legal matters in court.

rdf:Description.reg:name: judgeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is judge of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who hears and decides on legal matters in court to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: jurisdictionGoverned
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has jurisdiction governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a jurisdiction governed by a law, regulation, etc., that was enacted by another jurisdiction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: jurisdictionGovernedOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is jurisdiction governed of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a jurisdiction governed by a law, regulation, etc., that was enacted by another jurisdiction to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: key
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has key
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of pitch relationships that establishes a tonal centre, or principal tonal centre, of a musical resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: keyTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has key title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a unique name assigned to a resource by an ISSN registration agency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: landscapeArchitect
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has landscape architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an architect responsible for creating landscape resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: landscapeArchitectOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is landscape architect of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an architect responsible for creating landscape resources to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: languageOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a language an agent uses in its communications, when writing for publication, broadcasting, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: languageOfContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a language used to express the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: laterTitleProper
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has later title proper
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title proper appearing on a later issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial that differs from that on the first or earliest issue or part.

rdf:Description.reg:name: latitude
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has latitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a distance of a point on a planet or satellite measured north and south from the equator.

rdf:Description.reg:name: layout
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: letterer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has letterer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an illustrator contributing to a comic book, graphic novel, etc., by drawing text and graphic sound effects.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lettererOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is letterer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an illustrator contributing to a comic book, graphic novel, etc., by drawing text and graphic sound effects to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has librettist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an author of words of an opera or other musical stage resource or an oratorio.
