rdf:Description.reg:name: librettistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is librettist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an author of words of an opera or other musical stage resource or an oratorio to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: libretto
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides a text of an opera or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoBasedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a text of an opera or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource such as an opera or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that uses a text of a related resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lightingDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lighting designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by designing and creating lighting components.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lightingDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lighting designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by designing and creating lighting components to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lithographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lithographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by preparing a stone or plate for lithographic printing.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A lithographer includes a graphic artist creating a design directly on the surface from which printing will be done.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lithographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lithographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by preparing a stone or plate for lithographic printing.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A lithographer includes a graphic artist creating a design directly on the surface from which printing will be done.

rdf:Description.reg:name: localAffiliate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has local affiliate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a local agent affiliated with a broader agent which acts for it and others at a broader organizational level to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: locationOfConferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has location of conference, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a local place in which a conference, congress, meeting, exhibition, fair, festival, etc., was held.

rdf:Description.reg:name: longitude
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has longitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a distance of a point on a planet or satellite measured east and west from a reference meridian.

rdf:Description.reg:name: longitudeAndLatitude
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has longitude and latitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a system for identifying the area covered by the cartographic content of a resource using longitude of the westernmost and easternmost boundaries and latitude of the northernmost and southernmost boundaries.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lyricist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lyricist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an author of the words of a popular song, including a song or songs from a musical.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Authoring of just dialogue from a musical is excluded

rdf:Description.reg:name: lyricistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is lyricist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an author of the words of a popular song, including a song or songs from a musical to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: makeUpArtist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has make-up artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by applying make-up and prosthetics for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: makeUpArtistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is make-up artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by applying make-up and prosthetics for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manufacturer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manufacturer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manufacturerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is manufacturer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a resource in a published form to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manufacturersName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manufacturers name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of an agent responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manufactureStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying a place or places of manufacture, manufacturer or manufacturers, and date or dates of manufacture of a resource in a published form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediaType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has media type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting a general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: medium
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent held to be a channel of communication between the earthly world and a world of spirits.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediumOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is medium of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent held to be a channel of communication between the earthly world and a world of spirits to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediumOfPerformance
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an instrument, voice, or ensemble for which a musical resource was originally conceived.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediumOfPerformanceOfMusicalContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance of musical content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an instrument, voice, or ensemble used, or intended to be used, for performance of musical content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: member
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has member
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who is a member of an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: memberOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has member of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent of which an agent is a member to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergedToForm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merged to form
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource formed from a coming together of two or more resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mergee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a agent that merged with another agent to form a third to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that came together with one or more other resources to form a new resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: minuteTaker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has minute taker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for recording the minutes of a meeting.

rdf:Description.reg:name: minuteTakerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is minute taker of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for recording the minutes of a meeting to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mirrorSite
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is mirror site
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an exact copy of a website, used to reduce network traffic or improve the availability of the content of the original site.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mixingEngineer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mixing engineer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an audio engineer contributing to the audio content of a resource by manipulating, mixing, and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mixingEngineerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is mixing engineer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution to the audio content of manipulating, mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: modeOfIssuance
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mode of issuance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting whether a resource is issued in one or more parts, the way it is updated, and its intended termination.

rdf:Description.reg:name: moderator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has moderator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by leading a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.

rdf:Description.reg:name: moderatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is moderator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by leading a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: modifiedByVariationAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is modified by variation as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material taken from a source resource forms a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that is used in a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides text for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplayBasedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a screenplay for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mount
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has mount
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource has been attached.

rdf:Description.reg:name: music
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that is used in a motion picture, play, television program, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has musical director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by coordinating the activities of composers, sound editors, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by coordinating the activities of composers, sound editors, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalSettingOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides text for a non-dramatic musical resource, other than an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalTheatreAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical theatre adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a musical theatre resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource such as a motion picture, play, television program, etc., that uses a musical resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForMotionPicture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForRadioProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForTelevisionProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicProgrammer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has music programmer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a musical resource by using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The creation of a new musical resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicProgrammerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music programmer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a musical resource that incorporates a contribution of using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.

rdf:Description.reg:name: nameOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters by which an agent is known.

rdf:Description.reg:name: nameOfPlace
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters by which a place is known.

rdf:Description.reg:name: narrator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has narrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: narratorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is narrator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: natureOfContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has nature of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a specific character of a primary content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information associated with the recording, filming, etc., of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Note on capture includes the circumstances such as a live or studio recording, the equipment used, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnChangesInCarrierCharacteristics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in carrier characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on changes in the characteristics of a carrier that occur in subsequent issues or parts of a resource issued in successive parts or between iterations of an integrating resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnChangesInContentCharacteristics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in content characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on changes in content characteristics that occur in subsequent issues or parts of a resource issued in successive parts or between iterations of an integrating resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnCopyrightDate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on copyright date
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on copyright dates not recorded as part of a copyright date element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDimensionsOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the dimensions of a resource that is not recorded as part of a dimensions element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDistributionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of distribution, distributor, or date of distribution, or information on changes in the place of distribution, distributor, or distributors name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnEditionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on edition statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on a source of an edition statement, on edition statements relating to issues, parts, etc., on changes in edition statements, or other information relating to an edition statement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnExtentOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on extent of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the extent of a resource that is not recorded as part of an extent element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnFrequency
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on frequency
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on the currency of the contents, on the frequency of release of issues or parts of a serial or the frequency of updates to an integrating resource, or on changes in frequency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnIdentifierForResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on identifier for resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on identifiers for a resource not recorded as part of an identifier for a resource element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnIssuePartOrIterationUsedAsBasisForIdentificationOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on issue, part, or iteration used as basis for identification of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note identifying an issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial, or an iteration of an integrating resource that has been used as a basis for the identification of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnManufactureStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of manufacture, manufacturer, or date of manufacture, or information on changes in place of manufacture, manufacturer, or manufacturers name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnNumberingOfSerials
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on numbering of serials
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the numbering of the first or last issue or part, on complex or irregular numbering including numbering errors, on a period covered by a volume, issue, part, etc., or on other information relating to numbering of serials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnProductionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on production statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of production, producer, or date of production, or information on changes in place of production, producer, or producers name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnPublicationStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on publication statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of publication, publisher, or date of publication, information on changes in place of publication, publisher, or publishers name, or on suspension of publication.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing additional information about content recorded as a resource attribute.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnResourceSpecificCarrierCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on resource-specific carrier characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information about additional characteristics that are specific to a resource being described and are assumed not to apply to other resources exemplifying the same resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnSeriesStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on series statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on complex series statements, incorrect numbering within series, or changes in series statements.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnStatementOfResponsibility
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on statement of responsibility
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on an agent not named in a statement of responsibility to whom responsibility for the creation of, or contribution to a realization of, the intellectual or artistic content of a resource has been attributed, on variant forms of names appearing in the resource, on changes in statements of responsibility, or on other details relating to a statement of responsibility.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on a source from which a title was taken, on the date a title was viewed, on variations in titles, on inaccuracies, deletions, etc., or other information relating to a title.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelization
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a novel adapted from a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a novel.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingOfPart
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of part
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a larger resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption, and/or a chronological designation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingOfSerials
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of serials
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation for each of the issues or parts of a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingWithinSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a series.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingWithinSubseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a subseries.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberOfConferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has number of conference, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a conference, etc., within a series of conferences, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric and/or alphabetic designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in numeric or alphabetic form presented on the first issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric and/or alphabetic designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in numeric or alphabetic form presented on the last issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericDesignationOfMusicalResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric designation of musical resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical resource by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A numeric designation of a musical resource includes a caption such as e.g., no., op., BWV, and it may include a numeral, a letter, a word, any other character, or the combination of these.

rdf:Description.reg:name: officer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has officer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent holding an office in or commanding an agent to an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: officerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has officer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent holding an office in or commanding an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onDiscWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on disc with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is issued on the same disc with a resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenParticipant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has on-screen participant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a nonfiction moving image resource by taking an active role as a participant.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance on screen to provide contextual or background information is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenParticipantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on-screen participant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a nonfiction moving image resource by taking an active role as a participant to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance on screen to provide contextual or background information is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenPresenter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has on-screen presenter

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenPresenterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on-screen presenter of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by appearing on screen to provide contextual or background information. an on-screen presenter may appear in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Appearance in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials is included. Appearance on screen in a non-performing role is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: operaAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is opera adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as an opera.

rdf:Description.reg:name: oratorioAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is oratorio adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: organizer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has organizer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent organizing an exhibit, event, conference, course, program, etc., which gave rise to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: organizerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is organizer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent organizing an exhibit, event, conference, course, program, etc., which gave rise to a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherAgentAssociatedWithResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other agent associated with resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent other than a creator, custodian, owner, producer, publisher, distributor, or manufacturer associated with a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherAgentAssociatedWithResourceOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is other agent associated with resource of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent other than a creator, custodian, owner, producer, publisher, distributor or manufacturer associated with a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDesignationAssociatedWithAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other designation associated with agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, phrase, or abbreviation indicating incorporation or legal status of an agent, or any term serving to differentiate a an agent from other agents, etc., or a term other than a title that is associated with an agents name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDetailsOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other details of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of mathematical data and other features of the cartographic content of a resource not recorded in statements of scale, projection, and coordinates.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDistinguishingCharacteristicOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other distinguishing characteristic of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a characteristic other than form of resource, date of resource, place of origin of a resource, content type, or language of resource serving to differentiate a resource from another resource with the same title or from a name of an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherTitleInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other title information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title proper of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherTitleInformationOfSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other title information of series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title proper of a series.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherTitleInformationOfSubseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other title information of subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title proper of a subseries.

rdf:Description.reg:name: owner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent having legal possession of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: ownerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is owner of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent having legal possession of a resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: panelist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has panelist

rdf:Description.reg:name: reductionRatio

rdf:Description.reg:name: reductionRatioDesignation

rdf:Description.reg:name: referentialResourceRelationship

rdf:Description.reg:name: regionalEncoding

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedAgent

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is related to a resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remadeAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remade as

rdf:Description.reg:name: remakeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remake of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remixArtist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has remix artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating an audio resource by manipulating, recombining, mixing, and reproducing previously recorded sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remixArtistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remix artist of

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a later resource used in place of an earlier resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced in part by

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an earlier resource whose content has been partially replaced by a later resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an earlier resource whose content has been replaced by a later resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reprintedAs

rdf:Description.reg:name: reprintOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that reissues the same resource as a printed resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reproducedAs

rdf:Description.reg:name: reproductionOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: researcher

rdf:Description.reg:name: researcherOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: resolution

rdf:Description.reg:name: respondent

rdf:Description.reg:name: respondentOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is respondent of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a candidate for a degree who defends or opposes a thesis provided by a praeses in an academic disputation to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restorationist

rdf:Description.reg:name: restorationistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is restorationist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of a resource by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnAccess

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnUse

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewedIn

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is review of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a brief evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: revisedAs

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been updated, corrected, or expanded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: revisionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is revision of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for an updated, corrected, or expanded version.

rdf:Description.reg:name: rightAscension

rdf:Description.reg:name: rightAscensionAndDeclination
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has right ascension and declination
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a system for identifying the location of a celestial object in the sky covered by the cartographic content of a resource using angles of right ascension and declination.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scale
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has scale
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a ratio of the dimensions of the content of an image or three-dimensional form to the dimensions of the thing it represents

rdf:Description.reg:name: scaleDesignation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has scale designation

rdf:Description.reg:name: scaleOfStillImageOrThreeDimensionalForm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has scale of still image or three-dimensional form

rdf:Description.reg:name: scopeOfUsage

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayBasedOn

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayFor

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForMotionPicture

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTelevisionProgram

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForVideo

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenwriter

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenwriterOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an author of a screenplay, script, or scene to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: script

rdf:Description.reg:name: scriptForRadioProgram

rdf:Description.reg:name: sculptor

rdf:Description.reg:name: sculptorOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: seller

rdf:Description.reg:name: sellerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: separatedFrom

rdf:Description.reg:name: sequel

rdf:Description.reg:name: sequentialResourceRelationshipWith

rdf:Description.reg:name: seriesContainerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: setToMusicAs

rdf:Description.reg:name: singer

rdf:Description.reg:name: singerOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by using his/her/their voice, with or without instrumental accompaniment, to produce music. a singer's performance may or may not include actual words to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: softwareDeveloper

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by researching, designing, implementing, or testing software.

rdf:Description.reg:name: softwareDeveloperOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by researching, designing, implementing, or testing software to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: soundCharacteristic

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a presence or absence of sound in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: soundDesigner

rdf:Description.reg:name: soundDesignerOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by designing and creating audio/sound components to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: speakerOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by speaking words, such as a lecture, speech, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: specialEffectsProviderOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: specialIssue

rdf:Description.reg:name: specialIssueOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: specialPlaybackCharacteristic

rdf:Description.reg:name: splitInto

rdf:Description.reg:name: sponsor

rdf:Description.reg:name: sponsoringBody

rdf:Description.reg:name: sponsoringBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is sponsoring body of

rdf:Description.reg:name: stageDirector

rdf:Description.reg:name: storyteller

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by relaying a creator's original story with dramatic or theatrical interpretation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: storytellerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: summaryOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionScreenplayBasedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television screenplay based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a screenplay for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: termsOfAvailability
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has terms of availability
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a condition under which a publisher, distributor, etc., will normally supply a resource or the price of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: title
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters that names a resource or a resource embodied in it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word or phrase indicative of royalty, nobility, or ecclesiastical rank or office, a term of address for an agent of religious vocation, or another term indicative of rank, honour, or office.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters by which a resource is known.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleProper
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title proper
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a chief name of a resource, that is, a title normally used when naming a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An alternative title is treated as part of the title proper.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleProperOfSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title proper of series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of a series appearing on a resource of a part of a series.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleProperOfSubseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title proper of subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of a series appearing on a resource of a part of a subseries.

rdf:Description.reg:name: trackConfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has track configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a reource to a configuration of an audio track on a sound-track film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: transcriber
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transcriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by writing down or notating unwritten or unnotated content, or by changing it from one system of notation to another.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Transcription of a musical resource for a different instrument or performing group is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: transcriberOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is transcriber of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by writing down or notating previously unwritten or unnotated content, or by changing it from one system of notation to another to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Transcription of a musical resource for a different instrument or performing group is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translatedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that translates the text of a source entity into a language different from that of an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been translated, i.e., the text expressed in a language different from that of an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has translator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to an expression of a resource by expressing linguistic content of a resource in a language different from that of previous expressions of an original resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Translation of linguistic content between forms of the same language from different time periods is included.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by expressing linguistic content of a resource in a language different from that of previous expressions of an original resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Translation of linguistic content between forms of the same language from different time periods is included.

rdf:Description.reg:name: trustee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has trustee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an officer granted powers of administration in an agent in order to act for its benefit.

rdf:Description.reg:name: trusteeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is trustee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that grants powers of administration to an officer in order to act for its benefit.

rdf:Description.reg:name: typeOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has type of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization or generic descriptor for a type of agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: typeOfRecording
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has type of recording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a method used to encode audio content for playback.

rdf:Description.reg:name: undifferentiatedNameIndicator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has undifferentiated name indicator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization indicating that the core elements recorded are insufficient to differentiate between two or more agents with the same name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: uniformResourceLocator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has uniform resource locator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an address of an online resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A Uniform Resource Locators includes all resource identifiers intended to provide online access to a resource using a standard Internet browser.

rdf:Description.reg:name: variantNameForAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has variant name for agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name or form of name by which an agent is known that differs from a name or form of name chosen as a preferred name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: variantNameOfPlace
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has variant name of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a place to a name or form of name by which a place is known that differs from a name or form of name chosen as a preferred name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: variantTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has variant title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title associated with a resource that differs from a title recorded as a preferred title, title proper, a parallel title proper, other title information, parallel other title information, earlier title proper, later title proper, key title, or abbreviated title.

rdf:Description.reg:name: variationsBasedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is variations based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource from which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verseAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is verse adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a literary composition in verse form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verticalScaleOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has vertical scale of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a scale of elevation or vertical dimension of the cartographic content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted for video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has video characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a technical specification relating to an encoding of video images in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has video format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a standard, etc., used to encode the analog video content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoGameAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video game adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a video game.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical resource that is used in a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that provides text for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplayBasedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a screenplay for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: visualEffectsProvider
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has visual effects provider
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to an expression of a moving image resource by designing and creating post-production visual effects.

rdf:Description.reg:name: visualEffectsProviderOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is visual effects provider of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to an expression of a moving image resource by designing and creating post-production visual effects to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: voiceActor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has voice actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by providing a voice for characters in radio and audio productions and for animated characters in moving image resources as well as by providing voice-overs in radio and television commercials, dubbed resources, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: voiceActorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is voice actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by providing the voice for characters in radio and audio productions and for animated characters in moving image resources as well as by providing voice-overs in radio and television commercials, dubbed resources, etc. to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: wholePartResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has whole-part resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is contained in or contains another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedCommentary
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added commentary
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing an interpretation or critical explanation of an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedCommentaryOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of added commentary of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing an interpretation or critical explanation of an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedLyrics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added lyrics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a writer of words added to a musical resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Writing of lyrics in collaboration with a composer to form an original resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedLyricsOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of added lyrics of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a writer of words added to a musical resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Writing of lyrics in collaboration with a composer to form an original resource is excluded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedText
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added text
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a primarily non-textual resource by providing text, such as writing captions for photographs or descriptions of maps.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedTextOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of added text of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a primarily non-textual resource by providing text, such as captions for photographs or descriptions of maps to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAfterword
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of afterword
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing an afterword to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAfterwordOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of preface of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing a preface to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfForeword
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of foreword
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing a foreword to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfForewordOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of foreword of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing a foreword to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfIntroduction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of introduction
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing an introduction to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfIntroductionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of afterword of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing an afterword to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfPostface
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of postface
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing a postface to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfPostfaceOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of supplementary textual content of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing supplementary textual content (e.g., an appendix, an introduction, a preface) to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfPreface
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of preface
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing a preface to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfPrefaceOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of introduction of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing an introduction to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfSupplementaryTextualContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of supplementary textual content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by providing supplementary textual content (e.g., an appendix, an introduction, a preface) to an original resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfSupplementaryTextualContentOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is writer of postface of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by providing supplementary textual content, such as an introduction or a preface, to an original resource to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: yearDegreeGranted
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has year degree granted
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a calendar year in which a granting institution or faculty conferred an academic degree on a candidate.
